726896f-b.title: Queens: Home Lawn Street - Charlecote Ridge
726896f-b.text:
Home Lawn Street, at Charlecote Ridge, showing two views of the surrounding area. Grand Central Parkway was later cut through at the intersection of the two thoroughfares.
April 6, 1927
Views 1 and 2
P. L. Sperr
